text: We never actually met Sarah, as both parties were busy with SXSW, but she was very flexible and trusting in allowing us to do check-in and check-out ourselves. The listing is a very much lived-in apartment, and not a "destination" or a treat of some kind, but it was a perfectly acceptable place to come home to each night and in which to eat breakfast each morning during a hastily-planned last-minute trip to SXSW.
title: $150! 4.5m to ACL! 1B/1B.
